<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Strix c.a</title>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag    'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true %>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
  
</head>
<body>
    <div class="navbar navbar-fixed-top">
      <div class="container">
            <ul class="nav nav-tabs  nav-justified">  
              <li>
               <div id="logo" class="landscape" >
                 <a href="#">
                  <%= image_tag "logoandname.png" %> 
                  <!--<%= image_tag "strix-main.png" %> -->
                  </a>
              </div>
             </li>
             <li> <%= link_to "spam" , "#" %></li>
             <li> <%= link_to "Strix" , welcome_index_path %></li>
             <li> <%= link_to "9gag!", "https://9gag.com", :target => "_blank" %> </li>
             <li> <%= link_to "youtube!", "https://youtube.com", :target => "_blank" %> </li>
          </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="notification_zone ">
	<div class="container">
      <% if flash[:notice] %>
        <div class="alert alert-success">
          <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert">&times;</button>
          <%= flash[:notice] %>
        </div>
      <% elsif flash[:error] %>
        <div class="alert alert-error">
          <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert">&times;</button>
          <%= flash[:error] %>
        </div>
      <% elsif flash[:alert] %>
        <div class="alert">
          <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert">&times;</button>
          <%= flash[:alert] %>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div id="page-wrap" data-pjax-container=" ">
	<div class="over_content">
	    
	  <p><b>So, the leguend is true, the one who kills the ashbringer becomes the one</b></p>

        <!--here, on the yield statement is where most of the aplication info will display-->
        
        <%= yield %>

      
    </div>
  </div>
   
 
</body>
</html>
